{"tid":2498624,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"菅義偉向靖國神社供奉祭品    安倍晉三今日參拜    中方敦促日方反省侵略歷史","createTime":"2021-04-21T09:54:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T17:16:36.000Z","uid":141151,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"be20caf5dd32ba311b9d343559ed1ce819f39ed7","tid":2498624,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T09:54:08.000Z","msg":"菅義偉向靖國神社供奉祭品　中方敦促日方反省侵略歷史<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586949-20210421.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586949-20210421.htm&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dPYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=fc1eee43\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586949-20210421.htm&h=79533819\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586949-20210421.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">日本首相菅義偉在東京靖國神社開始的春季例行大祭之際，以 「內閣總理大臣菅義偉」名義供奉祭品。另外，前首相安倍晉三今日參拜了靖國神社。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人汪文斌回應說，靖國神社供奉著對日本對外侵略戰爭負有直接責任的二戰甲級戰犯。中方一貫堅決反對日本政要的錯誤做法，中方敦促日方恪守中日四個政治文件原則，切實落實中日四點原則共識，正視並深刻反省侵略歷史，同軍國主義劃清界限，以實際行動取信於亞洲鄰國和國際社會。"},{"pid":"42decf9dc4038779a0cec6d068d321a15956f540","tid":2498624,"uid":83328,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:02:28.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">支那又干涉別國內政</span>"},{"pid":"2bc497aff466ae22f6f952192c2c2736e1fe0afd","tid":2498624,"uid":227271,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:05:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTR73VFhhGXRyk8xchtWjcVmFLcU1evNCR7Pc7M5kNgY9?filename=UMAepKE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUMAepKE.jpg&h=4d01f5d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cef2bb119ce0cfecc9c4d795a3e7d85b35def176","tid":2498624,"uid":36157,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:22:24.